lu_seq_range Struct Reference
[lustreidl]

Describes a range of sequence, lsr_start is included but lsr_end is not in the range. More...

#include <lustre_idl.h>

Data Fields

__u64 lsr_start
__u64 lsr_end
__u32 lsr_index
__u32 lsr_flags

Detailed Description

Describes a range of sequence, lsr_start is included but lsr_end is not in the range.

Same structure is used in fld module where lsr_index field holds mdt id of the home mdt.
